---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <Fragment slot="breadcrumb">
    <Breadcrumb items={breadcrumbItems} />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Schema.org markup -->
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
    "name": "cTrader",
    "applicationCategory": "FinanceApplication",
    "operatingSystem": "Windows, macOS, iOS, Android, Web",
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "price": "0",
      "priceCurrency": "USD"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.6",
      "ratingCount": "15000"
    }
  })} />

  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": faqData.map(faq => ({
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": faq.question,
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": faq.answer
      }
    }))
  })} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="ctrader-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ctrader-hero-badge">
        <span class="badge-icon">üìà</span>
        <span>Professional ECN Trading Platform</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="heading-1">cTrader: The Ultimate Platform Review {currentYear}</h1>
      <p class="body-large ctrader-hero-sub">
        cTrader is a professional forex and CFD trading platform built for ECN execution. Full Level II pricing, built-in copy trading, and powerful automation with cTrader Automate.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-value">{ctraderBrokers.length}+</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">cTrader Brokers</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-value">ECN</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Execution</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-value">0.0</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Pips From</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-value">2011</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Since</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TrustBadges variant="light" compact={true} />

  <!-- Anchor Navigation -->
  <nav class="anchor-nav">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="anchor-links">
        {anchorItems.map((item) => (
          <a href={item.href} class="anchor-link">{item.text}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Best cTrader Brokers List -->
  <section class="section" id="brokers">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="heading-2">Best cTrader Brokers for {currentYear}</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Our top-rated brokers offering cTrader, ranked by spreads, execution, and overall value. All brokers are regulated and expert-reviewed.</p>

      <div class="broker-list">
        {ctraderBrokers.map((broker, index) => (
          <div class={`broker-card ${index === 0 ? 'broker-card--top' : ''}`}>
            {index === 0 && <span class="top-badge">Editor's Choice</span>}
            <div class="broker-card-rank">#{index + 1}</div>

            <div class="broker-card-main">
              <div class="broker-card-header">
                <h3 class="broker-name">{broker.name}</h3>
                <div class="broker-rating">
                  <span class="rating-score">{broker.scores.overall}</span>
                  <span class="rating-stars">{'‚òÖ'.repeat(Math.floor(broker.scores.overall))}</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="broker-tagline">{broker.tagline}</p>

              <div class="broker-stats">
                <div class="broker-stat">
                  <span class="stat-label">Spreads</span>
                  <span class="stat-value">{broker.spreadsFrom}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="broker-stat">
                  <span class="stat-label">Min Deposit</span>
                  <span class="stat-value">{broker.minDepositDisplay}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="broker-stat">
                  <span class="stat-label">Regulation</span>
                  <span class="stat-value">{broker.regulations[0]?.authority}</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="broker-pros">
                {broker.pros.slice(0, 3).map((pro) => (
                  <span class="pro-item">‚úì {pro}</span>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="broker-card-actions">
              <a href={broker.reviewUrl} class="btn btn-secondary">Read Review</a>
              <a href={broker.affiliateUrl} class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Visit Broker ‚Üí</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Broker Callout -->
  <aside class="broker-callout">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="callout-content">
        <div class="callout-text">
          <h3>Our #1 cTrader Broker: Pepperstone</h3>
          <p>FCA & ASIC regulated, raw spreads from 0.0 pips, full cTrader Copy support, and lightning-fast ECN execution.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/brokers/pepperstone" class="btn btn-primary">Visit Pepperstone ‚Üí</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <!-- What is cTrader Section -->
  <section class="section section--alt" id="what-is-ctrader">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2 class="heading-2">What is cTrader?</h2>
          <p>
            cTrader is a professional-grade forex and CFD trading platform developed by Spotware Systems. Launched in 2011, it was built from the ground up for ECN/STP trading - meaning direct market access with no dealing desk intervention.
          </p>
          <p>
            Unlike MetaTrader 4 which was originally designed for market makers, cTrader was created specifically for traders who want transparent pricing. You see real market depth with Level II pricing, get true interbank spreads, and experience fast execution without requotes.
          </p>
          <p>
            cTrader includes features that MT4 requires third-party plugins for: built-in copy trading (cTrader Copy), algorithmic trading environment (cTrader Automate), and a fully-featured web platform that runs in any browser.
          </p>
          <p>
            The platform is available for desktop (Windows and Mac), web browser, and mobile devices (iOS and Android). All versions share the same modern interface and feature set, so you can trade seamlessly across devices.
          </p>

          <h3>cTrader Summary</h3>
          <p>
            cTrader is the platform of choice for serious traders who prioritize execution quality and market transparency. The Level II pricing shows you exactly where the liquidity is, the modern interface feels intuitive from day one, and features like one-click trading speed up your workflow.
          </p>
          <p>
            The main trade-off compared to MT4 is ecosystem size. While cTrader has a growing community of cBot developers and signal providers, it can't match MT4's massive library of Expert Advisors and indicators built over 18+ years. However, for traders who want ECN execution and modern features, cTrader is hard to beat.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="quick-facts">
            <h3>cTrader Quick Facts</h3>
            <dl>
              <dt>Released</dt>
              <dd>2011</dd>
              <dt>Developer</dt>
              <dd>Spotware Systems</dd>
              <dt>Cost</dt>
              <dd>Free</dd>
              <dt>Best For</dt>
              <dd>ECN, Scalping</dd>
              <dt>Platforms</dt>
              <dd>Win, Mac, Web, Mobile</dd>
              <dt>Language</dt>
              <dd>C# (cBots)</dd>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="cta-box">
            <h4>Start Trading on cTrader</h4>
            <p><strong>Pepperstone</strong> offers cTrader with:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Raw spreads from 0.0 pips</li>
              <li>FCA & ASIC regulated</li>
              <li>Full cTrader Copy support</li>
              <li>Fast ECN execution</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/brokers/pepperstone" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Visit Pepperstone</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pros and Cons -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="heading-2 text-center">Should You Use cTrader?</h2>
      <p class="section-intro text-center">Based on expert testing and hands-on use, here's what traders think of cTrader:</p>

      <div class="pros-cons-grid">
        <div class="pros-card">
          <h3>‚úÖ 8 Reasons To Use cTrader</h3>
          <ul>
            {reasonsToUse.map((reason) => (
              <li>{reason}</li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="cons-card">
          <h3>‚õî 3 Reasons To Consider Alternatives</h3>
          <ul>
            {reasonsNotToUse.map((reason) => (
              <li>{reason}</li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Features Table -->
  <section class="section section--alt" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="heading-2 text-center">cTrader Key Features</h2>
      <p class="section-intro text-center">cTrader is a feature-rich platform built for professional traders. Here's how it performs:</p>

      <div class="features-table-wrapper">
        <table class="features-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Feature</th>
              <th>cTrader Performance</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {keyFeatures.map((item) => (
              <tr>
                <td><span class="feature-icon">{item.icon}</span> {item.feature}</td>
                <td>{item.performance}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Cards -->
      <div class="feature-cards">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>cTrader Trading System</h3>
          <p>Built for fast ECN execution with sophisticated order management:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Market, limit, stop, and stop-limit orders</li>
            <li>Trailing stops with server-side execution</li>
            <li>One-click trading with quick SL/TP</li>
            <li>Partial close and position management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>cTrader Analytics</h3>
          <p>Advanced charting and analysis tools for technical traders:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>70+ built-in technical indicators</li>
            <li>26 timeframes (including tick charts)</li>
            <li>Detachable multi-monitor charts</li>
            <li>Drawing tools and pattern recognition</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- cTrader vs MT4 -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="heading-2 text-center">cTrader vs MetaTrader 4</h2>
      <p class="section-intro text-center">The two most popular retail trading platforms compared side by side:</p>

      <div class="comparison-table-wrapper">
        <table class="comparison-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Feature</th>
              <th>cTrader</th>
              <th>MetaTrader 4</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Depth of Market</td>
              <td class="highlight">Full Level II pricing</td>
              <td>Limited</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Execution Model</td>
              <td class="highlight">ECN/STP native</td>
              <td>Varies by broker</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Timeframes</td>
              <td class="highlight">26 timeframes</td>
              <td>9 timeframes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Built-in Indicators</td>
              <td class="highlight">70+</td>
              <td>30+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Copy Trading</td>
              <td class="highlight">Built-in (cTrader Copy)</td>
              <td>Third-party only</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Automation Language</td>
              <td>C# (cAlgo)</td>
              <td class="highlight">MQL4 (larger community)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Broker Support</td>
              <td>Limited selection</td>
              <td class="highlight">Very wide</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Third-party Tools</td>
              <td>Growing</td>
              <td class="highlight">Massive ecosystem</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Interface</td>
              <td class="highlight">Modern, clean design</td>
              <td>Dated but functional</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Web Platform</td>
              <td class="highlight">Full-featured</td>
              <td>Basic</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="comparison-note">
        <strong>Bottom line:</strong> Choose cTrader for transparent ECN pricing, Level II market depth, modern interface, and built-in copy trading. Choose MT4 for maximum broker choice and access to thousands of third-party EAs and indicators.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detailed Features (Collapsible) -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="heading-2 text-center">cTrader Features In-Depth</h2>
      <p class="section-intro text-center">Explore cTrader's key features in detail:</p>

      <div class="accordion-list">
        <details class="accordion-item">
          <summary class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">üìä</span>
            <span class="accordion-title">Level II Pricing (Depth of Market)</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Level II pricing is one of cTrader's standout features. Unlike basic bid/ask quotes, Level II shows you the full order book - all pending buy and sell orders at different price levels.</p>
            <p>This transparency helps you understand real market liquidity, see where large orders are sitting, and identify potential support and resistance levels based on actual order flow.</p>
            <p>The DOM (Depth of Market) panel in cTrader displays this visually, showing order sizes at each price level. You can trade directly from the DOM by clicking price levels to place orders.</p>
            <div class="broker-note">
              <strong>Why it matters:</strong> With Level II, you're seeing the same information that institutional traders see. No more guessing about liquidity or market depth.
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="accordion-item">
          <summary class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">üë•</span>
            <span class="accordion-title">cTrader Copy (Social Trading)</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>cTrader Copy is the built-in social trading system that lets you automatically replicate trades from successful strategy providers. It's fully integrated into the platform - no third-party plugins required.</p>
            <p>As a copier, you can browse strategy providers, view their detailed performance statistics (win rate, drawdown, profit factor), and allocate funds to copy their trades automatically. You control your risk with equity-based position sizing.</p>
            <p>As a strategy provider, you can share your trading strategies and earn commissions when others copy you. cTrader handles all the tracking and attribution automatically.</p>
            <div class="broker-note">
              <strong>Broker Tip:</strong> <a href="/brokers/pepperstone">Pepperstone</a> and <a href="/brokers/ic-markets">IC Markets</a> offer full cTrader Copy support with a good selection of strategy providers.
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="accordion-item">
          <summary class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">ü§ñ</span>
            <span class="accordion-title">cTrader Automate (cBots & Custom Indicators)</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>cTrader Automate (formerly known as cAlgo) is the algorithmic trading environment that lets you create custom indicators and automated trading robots (cBots).</p>
            <p>Unlike MT4's MQL4, cTrader Automate uses C# - a powerful, modern programming language. This gives you access to the full .NET framework, meaning you can integrate with databases, web APIs, and other systems that would be difficult in MQL4.</p>
            <p>cTrader includes a built-in code editor with IntelliSense, debugging tools, and backtesting capabilities. You can also download pre-built cBots from the cTrader community.</p>
            <p><strong>Key capabilities:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>Create custom indicators and cBots using C#</li>
              <li>Full .NET framework access for advanced integrations</li>
              <li>Built-in backtester with optimization</li>
              <li>Access to market data, account info, and order management APIs</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="broker-note">
              <strong>Learning curve:</strong> If you know any C-style language (C#, Java, JavaScript), you'll pick up cBot development quickly. The <a href="https://ctrader.com/ctrader-automate/guides" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official cTrader Automate documentation</a> is excellent.
            </div>
          </div>
